casebody.data:
RIVER PARK RESIDENCES, LP, Respondent,
v.
RICHMAN PLAZA GARAGE CORP., Appellant, et al., Respondents. Motion No: 2017-1042 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided on December 19, 2017

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the Court of Appeals does not have jurisdiction to entertain this motion for leave to appeal from an order entered in this proceeding commenced in Civil Court of the City of New York (see NY Const, art VI, § 3 [b][7]; CPLR 5602[a] ).
